{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01HLEQMguwmBhMkMNJ2fWi4b","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012oivvcXEjFD2quLy6CUehW","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/commands/AGENTS.md","old_string":"### validate-state.ts","new_string":"### validate-schema.ts\nCLI subcommand: `codeharness validate schema`. Validates workflow YAML files against JSON schemas using `parseWorkflow()`. Accepts a path or directory, validates each `.yaml`/`.yml` file, and reports results.\n- **Key deps:** `lib/workflow-parser` (parseWorkflow, WorkflowParseError), `lib/output`\n- **Exports:** `registerValidateSchemaCommand(parent)`\n\n### validate-self.ts\nCLI subcommand: `codeharness validate self`. Runs self-validation cycle and produces a release gate report. Initializes a validation sprint, loops through `runValidationCycle()` until no actionable ACs remain, then outputs a summary. Outputs \"RELEASE GATE: PASS -- v1.0 ready\" when all non-blocked ACs pass.\n- **Key deps:** `modules/verify` (createValidationSprint, runValidationCycle, getValidationProgress, getACById), `lib/output`\n- **Exports:** `registerValidateSelfCommand(parent)`\n\n### validate-state.ts"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":630,"cache_read_input_tokens":53482,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":630},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"87824d62-8d3a-42e8-9563-dae1782fbf60","uuid":"bf3fb736-a15f-4be5-9cda-fe2bc6ae0e39"}
