{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AoN3QTETsTu3xZwos2MxJg","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"87824d62-8d3a-42e8-9563-dae1782fbf60","uuid":"1f2954b5-4e39-4353-a91f-681090c92356","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:35:06.769Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","oldString":"### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — create-story (2026-04-02T15:12)","newString":"### 3-2-embedded-agent-templates — create-story (2026-04-02T15:32)\n\n- **Risks:** AC 6 (\"derive from BMAD definitions\") is structurally verifiable but semantic derivation quality harder to test automatically.\n- **Observations:** BMAD tech-writer agent lives in subdirectory unlike other 7 flat agents. No BMAD evaluator agent — purely codeharness concept. BMAD persona.principles uses pipe-delimited strings in some agents, arrays in others.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Read: 8, Glob: 5, Grep: 4, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `ls templates/` (~18 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 10 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — create-story (2026-04-02T15:12)","originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — state recovery (2026-04-02T15:30)\n\n- **State sync issue:** Story 3-1 was fully implemented, reviewed, and verified (ALL_PASS 8/8) with commit 631a003 but sprint-state.json still showed `backlog`. Previous session completed the work but failed to update state.\n- **AGENTS.md stale:** src/commands/AGENTS.md was missing entries for validate-schema.ts and validate-self.ts (from story 2-5). Fixed by adding both entries.\n- **Recovery action:** Manually updated sprint-state.json and ran codeharness verify to transition to done.\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — create-story (2026-04-02T15:12)\n\n- **Ambiguity in epic definition:** PRD overhaul has different FR numbering than prd-evaluator-redesign.md and epics-v2.md. Used epics-v2.md + prd-evaluator-redesign.md as canonical sources.\n- **No config.yaml at expected location:** `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` exists but `_bmad/config.yaml` (referenced by workflow) does not. Minor path inconsistency.\n- **Sprint-status.yaml not updated by subagent:** Per instruction, subagent did not modify sprint-status.yaml. Orchestrator handles status transitions.\n- **No project-context.md found:** Only templates exist. No material impact.\n- **Observations:** All 8 ACs are `test-provable` — purely schema definition + validation function story.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 19\n- By tool: Read: 9, Grep: 5, Glob: 4, Bash: 1, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `git log --oneline -10` (~10 lines)\n- Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — verification (2026-04-02T15:30)\n\n- **codeharness verify precondition failure:** Stale AGENTS.md for src/commands module (missing validate-schema.ts, validate-self.ts from story 2-5). Pre-existing issue, unrelated to story 3-1.\n- **AC7 weak evidence:** Schema importable verified via source-level check only, not runtime import. Expected since it's internal-only.\n- **validateAgentSchema not in dist/:** Not re-exported from CLI entry point. Internal-only, matches story intent.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 3, Grep: 3, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: vitest verbose (~60 lines), npm test:unit (~40 lines), vitest coverage (~30 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Ran vitest coverage twice\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — code-review (2026-04-02T15:24)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- MEDIUM: Schema accepted empty strings for name, role.title, role.purpose, persona.identity, persona.communication_style, principles items — fixed with minLength: 1\n- MEDIUM: Schema accepted empty principles array — fixed with minItems: 1\n- MEDIUM: Schema accepted personality: {} without traits — fixed by making traits required\n- MEDIUM: Tests missing for empty string, personality without traits, empty principles, non-string disallowedTools — all added\n\n**Code quality issues NOT fixed (LOW):**\n- validateAgent internal variable naming clarity\n- disallowedTools could benefit from minItems: 1 (debatable)\n\n**Coverage:** 96.65% overall, schema-validate.ts at 100%.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 5, Edit: 7, Grep: 1, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: vitest verbose (~40 lines), codeharness coverage (~5 lines), git diff (~25 lines)\n- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Coverage command ran twice\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — dev-story (2026-04-02T15:18)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 4, Edit: 5, Write: 2, Glob: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` full suite (~500+ lines), `npx tsc --noEmit` (~3 lines)\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":6,"oldLines":6,"newStart":6,"newLines":18,"lines":[" - **AGENTS.md stale:** src/commands/AGENTS.md was missing entries for validate-schema.ts and validate-self.ts (from story 2-5). Fixed by adding both entries."," - **Recovery action:** Manually updated sprint-state.json and ran codeharness verify to transition to done."," ","+### 3-2-embedded-agent-templates — create-story (2026-04-02T15:32)","+","+- **Risks:** AC 6 (\"derive from BMAD definitions\") is structurally verifiable but semantic derivation quality harder to test automatically.","+- **Observations:** BMAD tech-writer agent lives in subdirectory unlike other 7 flat agents. No BMAD evaluator agent — purely codeharness concept. BMAD persona.principles uses pipe-delimited strings in some agents, arrays in others.","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 16","+- By tool: Read: 8, Glob: 5, Grep: 4, Bash: 1, Write: 1","+- Largest Bash outputs: `ls templates/` (~18 lines)","+- Files read: 10 unique, 10 total reads","+- Redundant operations: None","+"," ### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — create-story (2026-04-02T15:12)"," "," - **Ambiguity in epic definition:** PRD overhaul has different FR numbering than prd-evaluator-redesign.md and epics-v2.md. Used epics-v2.md + prd-evaluator-redesign.md as canonical sources."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
