n- **Method:** `validateAgentSchema()` is exported from `src/lib/schema-validate.ts`; test suite calls it for all 9 agents\n- **Evidence:** 85 tests in `embedded-agent-templates.test.ts` all pass, including 9 schema validation tests\n- **Test coverage:** 9 tests in \"schema validation (AC #3)\" describe block — all pass\n- **Result:** PASS\n\n### AC #4: evaluator.yaml has disallowedTools and anti-leniency principles\n- **Method:** Direct file read of `templates/agents/evaluator.yaml`\n- **Evidence:**\n  - `disallowedTools: [\"Edit\", \"Write\"]` present (lines 19-21)\n  - `persona.principles` contains: \"Never give the benefit of the doubt\", \"Every PASS requires evidence\", \"UNKNOWN if unable to verify\", \"Re-verify from scratch\", \"Report exactly what was observed\"\n- **Test coverage:** Tests for disallowedTools and anti-leniency keywords — all pass\n- **Result:** PASS\n\n### AC #5: evaluator.yaml personality traits (rigor >= 0.9, warmth <= 0.3)\n- **Method:** Direct file read of `templates/agents/evaluator.yaml`\n- **Evidence:** `rigor: 0.98` (>= 0.9), `warmth: 0.2` (<= 0.3), `directness: 0.95`\n- **Test coverage:** Tests for trait range assertions — all pass\n- **Result:** PASS\n\n### AC #6: Embedded templates derive from BMAD but use codeharness format\n- **Method:** Node.js script checked all 9 files for absence of BMAD-specific keys (`agent`, `metadata`, `menu`, `critical_actions`, `prompts`)\n- **Evidence:** All 9 files report `bad_keys=none`; all use flat YAML format with top-level `name`, `role`, `persona`\n- **Test coverage:** 16 BMAD cross-reference tests — all pass\n- **Result:** PASS\n\n### AC #7: package.json files array includes templates/agents/\n- **Method:** `grep \"templates/agents/\" package.json`\n- **Evidence:** Line 22: `\"templates/agents/\"` present in files array\n- **Result:** PASS\n\n### AC #8: Unit tests pass covering all required scenarios\n- **Method:** `npm run test:unit` with verbose reporter\n- **Evidence:** 85 tests in `embedded-agent-templates.test.ts` — all pass. Covers: file existence (9), YAML parsing (9), required fields (9), schema validation (9), name-filename matching (9), evaluator disallowedTools, evaluator anti-leniency, evaluator personality traits, BMAD cross-references (16). No regressions (3757 total tests pass).\n- **Result:** PASS\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| AC | Description | Result |\n|----|-------------|--------|\n| #1 | 9 YAML files exist | PASS |\n| #2 | Required top-level fields | PASS |\n| #3 | Schema validation | PASS |\n| #4 | Evaluator disallowedTools + anti-leniency | PASS |\n| #5 | Evaluator personality traits | PASS |\n| #6 | BMAD derivation, codeharness format | PASS |\n| #7 | package.json files array | PASS |\n| #8 | Unit tests comprehensive | PASS |\n\n**Final verdict: ALL_PASS (8/8 ACs)**\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2456,"cache_read_input_tokens":30691,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2456,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01JdbSnbQe7A8sUhDYyjxMAG","session_id":"87824d62-8d3a-42e8-9563-dae1782fbf60","uuid":"55112815-e55b-477f-be6f-73b6f308623b"}
