{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019Ww1eCeBTnELJirrdSybDK","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02\n2\t\n3\t### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — state recovery (2026-04-02T15:30)\n4\t\n5\t- **State sync issue:** Story 3-1 was fully implemented, reviewed, and verified (ALL_PASS 8/8) with commit 631a003 but sprint-state.json still showed `backlog`. Previous session completed the work but failed to update state.\n6\t- **AGENTS.md stale:** src/commands/AGENTS.md was missing entries for validate-schema.ts and validate-self.ts (from story 2-5). Fixed by adding both entries.\n7\t- **Recovery action:** Manually updated sprint-state.json and ran codeharness verify to transition to done.\n8\t\n9\t### 3-2-embedded-agent-templates — verification (2026-04-02T15:50)\n10\t\n11\t- **Workaround:** Initial proof document format not recognized by codeharness verify parser — rewrote in expected format.\n12\t- **Verification gap:** AC #3 (schema validation) verified indirectly through test pass status rather than standalone Node script.\n13\t- **Observations:** Test count 85 matches post-review, total suite 3757.\n14\t\n15\t## Token Report\n16\t- Total tool calls: 18\n17\t- By tool: Bash: 12, Read: 3, Grep: 2, Write: 1\n18\t- Largest Bash outputs: vitest verbose (~30 lines), test:unit (~60 lines), coverage (~30 lines)\n19\t- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n20\t- Redundant operations: Coverage run twice, verbose test grep attempted 3 times\n21\t\n22\t### 3-2-embedded-agent-templates — code-review (2026-04-02T15:42)\n23\t\n24\t**Bugs found:**\n25\t- MEDIUM (fixed): No BMAD cross-reference test for AC #6 — only structural checks, no content derivation validation. Added 16 tests.\n26\t- MEDIUM (fixed): Redundant filesystem reads in tests (~50 per run) — added Map cache.\n27\t- LOW (not fixed): role.purpose derivation inconsistent across templates (some verbatim, some expanded)\n28\t- LOW (not fixed): Template YAML files