{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011So6Wf1QGQYftGDCeTW8R1","type":"tool_result","content":"1765\t| 6 | Consider batch maintenance session to clear all recurring LOW issues from sessions 1-8 | MEDIUM | planning | 1 hr |\n1766\t\n1767\t---\n1768\t\n1769\t**Session 8 verdict:** Cleanest session yet. One story, zero failures, zero retries, real bugs caught by review. The harness process is maturing — the main remaining waste is tooling fragility (`codeharness stats`) and accumulated documentation staleness.\n1770\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01EVEwabib88yD4bP88znb2u","session_id":"87824d62-8d3a-42e8-9563-dae1782fbf60","uuid":"a614530d-903c-4bba-a551-d76793570bfe","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:50:04.755Z"}
